{"type": "article", "id": 5858, "title": "爆米花机 Popcorn Monsoon", "description": "", "date": "2015-02-04T07:44:58Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 13, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234033hl2IiyGm3xQ04B9V.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t毕业于埃因霍温设计学院的设计师 Jolene Carlier 日前推出了一款全新设计的爆米花机 Popcorn Monsoon。这款造型特别且充满童趣的爆米花机由一个浅粉色的底座、两个黄色的杯状容器以及一条透明的 U 型管道组成。整个机器的利用热气取代燃油的原理进行加热，然后爆米花便能够通过透明管道输出，做法简单又快捷。如需购买，请联系 <a href=\"mailto:jolene.carlier@gmail.com\">jolene.carlier@gmail.com</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<iframe height=\"498\" width=\"640\" src=\"http://player.youku.com/embed/XODg1ODUyNDMy\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\">\r\n</iframe>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234032KjWCXQikGxwEz65l.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}